{"id":13,"date":"2026-04-21T18:34:54","date_gmt":"2026-04-21T18:34:54","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost\/?page_id=13"},"modified":"2026-04-22T19:27:39","modified_gmt":"2026-04-22T19:27:39","slug":"how-to-connect-to-shh","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/localhost\/","title":{"rendered":"How to connect to SHH"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light has-contrast-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-9e6f72258a00cad2bd77c4d79fa726ee\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-base-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-cover-is-layout-873ee6b1 wp-block-cover-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-7ee84d44 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:65%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-stretch is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-353c4f5a wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:35%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-stretch is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-73b0033c wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right has-x-large-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.2\"><br><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"615\" height=\"437\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-1.png 615w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-1-300x213.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Go to the Ubuntu <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>server website<br>and download the<br>server version<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also download the<br>desktop version<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"613\" height=\"252\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-17\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-2.png 613w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-2-300x123.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 613px) 100vw, 613px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Open up hyper V<br>in select new<br>virtual machine<br>than name it<br>Ubuntu server<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"615\" height=\"323\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-3.png 615w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-3-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Give it 4096mb of<br>memory<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"611\" height=\"501\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-4.png 611w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-4-300x246.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click default<br>switch<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Than click on your<br>server for the<br>image file<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"41\" height=\"41\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-20\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Do the samething<br>for the desktop<br>verison<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"622\" height=\"235\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-21\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-6.png 622w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-6-300x113.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 622px) 100vw, 622px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Find your<br>windows server IP<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"616\" height=\"280\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-22\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-7.png 616w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-7-300x136.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On your linux<br>desktop type ssh<br>linuxuser@your ip<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"616\" height=\"280\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-23\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-8.png 616w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-8-300x136.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Exit out than enter<br>the command ssh-<br>keygen -t rsa -b<br>4096 than click<br>enter twice<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"616\" height=\"280\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-24\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-9.png 616w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-9-300x136.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 616px) 100vw, 616px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now enter ssh-<br>copy-id<br>linuxuser@172.23<br>.10.154 than click<br>enter<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"621\" height=\"249\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-10.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-25\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-10.png 621w, http:\/\/localhost\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/04\/image-10-300x120.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you should<br>be able to login<br>without a<br>password<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check to see<br>you\u2019re able to<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>login without a<br>password<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Go to the Ubuntu server websiteand download theserver version Also download thedesktop version Open up hyper Vin select newvirtual machinethan name itUbuntu server Give it 4096mb ofmemory Click defaultswitch Than click on yourserver for theimage file Do the samethingfor the desktopverison Find yourwindows server IP On your linuxdesktop type sshlinuxuser@your ip Exit out than enterthe [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-13","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost\/index.php\/wp-j